order_number.orig_str: शासन निर्णय क्रमांकः स्थापना-२०२४/ प्र.क्र.२४७/ आरोग्य-४

para_trans: G. Kannada and Paithan taluks of Sambhajinagar district (Mauje Nimbora, Mauje Adgaon Pishor, Ta. Kannada and Mauje Indegaon, Ta. Paithan) regarding the sanction of a new health sub-centre here.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.247 / Health-4

Read: - Letter from Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries) Mumbai No: Hospital / Room-7A / T-5 / Sub-Centre / Establishment / G. Sambhajinagar / 2739-41/2024, dated 11.07.2024.

Introduction: - In Kannada and Paithan taluks of Sambhajinagar district (Mauje Nimbora, Mauje Adgaon Pishor, Ta. Kannada and Mauje Indegaon, Ta. The matter of sanctioning a new sub-station at Paithan) was under consideration of the government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:

Government Decision: - g. Kannada and Paithan Taluks in Sambhajinagar District (Mauje Nimbora, Mauje Adgaon Pishor, Ta. Kannada and Mauje Indegaon, Ta. The sanction of a new health sub-centre at Paithan) is being approved under this Government decision.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
